{"tid":1700910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"挪威電視台想搵被捕人士做訪問，唔出樣","createTime":"2019-11-08T17:50:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T06:59:38.000Z","uid":110256,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"ef8c50b3f067aedbd5515ac925b40c5b4bcf6bed","tid":1700910,"uid":110256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T17:50:23.000Z","msg":"［代fd出po，佢有個外國朋友係記者］<br />\nNorway TV搵緊一啲年輕嘅被捕人士做訪問。<br />\n希望你能夠幫到手，等外國傳媒都知道香港發生嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n內容：<br />\n訪問主要係想講返佢嘅<strong>被捕經過</strong>；<br />\n想訪問埋被捕者<strong>父母屋企人對佢被捕嘅感受</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n*唔使出樣，會就角度；聲音經過處理，<br />\n會有翻譯，可以講返中文的。<br />\n可以嘅麻煩Telegram聯絡：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/boboboyboy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fboboboyboy5&d=zUJDlVqOtbKZlRnsKtUQBJq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=fae76ead\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/boboboyboy5</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！"},{"pid":"7ad086f2d8cd0de49bef077128dd98f5203600b8","tid":1700910,"uid":110256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T18:04:59.000Z","msg":"self tui"},{"pid":"c298af72d64ed663f3ff13d746a6e6dcb24c5ad0","tid":1700910,"uid":110256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T18:05:10.000Z","msg":"self tui"},{"pid":"33677153ed2100b398569aa670245dfb0bb8274d","tid":1700910,"uid":110256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T18:12:45.000Z","msg":"self tui"},{"pid":"ac982da2f393513a9b2e8d1f307f8d7a6fff8e91","tid":1700910,"uid":4355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T18:15:23.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e34b70dc9aa898a14665ac01cd652cc6971182e8","tid":1700910,"uid":116976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T18:22:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b175148bacd3c9bb7ffef478493b5